commit.message:
re PR c/7652 (-Wswitch-break : Warn if a switch case falls through)

	PR c/7652
	* config/i386/i386.c (ix86_expand_args_builtin): Add break.
	(ix86_expand_round_builtin): Likewise.

From-SVN: r238864
